<li>顶部对齐确定顶部的位置<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/1%E9%A1%B6%E9%83%A8%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%A1%B6%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE.png" alt=""></li>
<li>左对齐确定图片的最左边<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/2.%E5%B7%A6%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%B7%A6%E8%BE%B9.png" alt=""></li>
<li>右对齐确定图片的最右边<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/3.%E5%8F%B3%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%80%E5%8F%B3%E8%BE%B9.png" alt=""></li>
<li>纵向分布确定纵向图片间的间距<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/4.%E7%BA%B5%E5%90%91%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%BA%B5%E5%90%91%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D.png" alt=""></li>
<li>横向分布确定横向图片间的间距<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/5.%E6%A8%AA%E5%90%91%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%A8%AA%E5%90%91%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D.png" alt=""></li>
<li>组合上述已经调整好的横纵向分布图片组合为一张大图<br><img src="http://ot0ad32fs.bkt.clouddn.com/6.%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8A%E8%BF%B0%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%AA%E7%BA%B5%E5%90%91%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%A0%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%BE.png" alt=""></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>PS、AI组图请看下集！</strong></p>
]]></content>
    
